title: Africa Union’s free trade area a step closer to fruition
description: The African Continental Free Trade Agreement is now a step closer to fruition after a review of the draft and consultation with industry players, and experts. Ahead of the signing due on Wednesday, CNBC Africa spoke to the AU Commissioner for Trade and Industry H.E. Albert M. Muchanga on possible bottlenecks.
